<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <title>Flux API</title>

        <!-- Viewport mobile tag for sensible mobile support -->
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1">

<!-- Monitoring test content
repo=<%= sails.config.git.repoSlug  %>
branch=<%= sails.config.git.branch  %>
commit=<%= sails.config.git.commit %>
dokkuApp=<%= process.env.DOKKU_APP_NAME %>
-->
        <style>
            body, html {
                font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
                color: #1a1a1a;
            }

            a {
                text-decoration: none;
                color: #00b8d4;
            }

            .HomePage {
                height: 100%;
                padding: 0;
                margin: 0;
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .HomePage > div {
                max-width: 600px;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .HomePage > div > h2 {
                font-size: 7em;
                font-weight: normal;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .HomePage__button {
                display: inline-block;
                text-decoration: none;
                color: #fff;
                background-color: #37474f;
                border-radius: 2px;
                padding: 0 16px;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                height: 36px;
                line-height: 36px;
                box-shadow: 0px 1px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12), 0px 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
                transition: all 450ms cubic-bezier(0.23, 1, 0.32, 1) 0ms;
                font-size: 14px;
                text-transform: uppercase;
            }

            .HomePage__button:hover {
                background-color: #879196;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="HomePage">
            <div>
                <h2>Flux API</h2>
                <p>
                    Vous vous trouvez sur serveur de donnée de Flux. Il n'y a pas d'autres pages que celle-ci, mais si vous êtes intéressé par le projet, vous pouvez consulter le code source sur <a href="http://github.com/ungdev/flux2-server">Github</a>.
                </p>
                <a href="https://bar.utt.fr" class="HomePage__button">
                    Aller sur Flux
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
